description:
This is a 30 minute workout called '30 Minute Rhythm Cycling Class - Intermediate Dance Ride' from the channel Gabriella Guevara.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Nightclub Workout and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.
